In November of 2017, Amazon approved the True Reply skill to collect consumer feedback via Alexa-powered devices, exposing the True Reply platform to more than 36 million households. Anyone with an Amazon Echo or similar device can earn rewards by taking surveys at their own convenience just by using their voice..
`_ `_______ `_ `____ `_____ `_______ `__ `___ `____ `____ `_ `______ `_______ `_______ `__ `____________ `_______ `_______ `__ `___ `____ `_______ `_ `___ `___ `_ `______ `__________ `_____ `___ `_ `_____ `___ `_ `______ `_____ `__ `___ `______ `_ `_____ `______ `_ `____ `__ `__________ `___ `_ `____ `____ `______ 
While earnings on the True Reply platform can be cashed out via PayPal, the addition of a blockchain-based digital currency brings the opportunity to eliminate fees and streamline transactions on the platform. The ability to earn the True Reply platform's TrueCoin token helps to bring cryptocurrency mainstream by removing risks associated with buying cryptocurrency since users are now able to earn the token simply by participating via any telephone or any Amazon Alexa-powered device..
