An example of the power of voice-based interface was on display at last month's CES 2018 conference in Las Vegas, where Ford and Toyota demonstrated Alexa integrations in their vehicles. Motorists will soon be earning rewards using Alexa via True Reply while they're stuck in traffic or running errands..
