The implications for market research are staggering. All True Reply survey responses can be listened to individually, allowing researchers to drill down into specific responses and deepen their understanding of how people think about a product or service. The market for the platform will rapidly surpass the current $16 billion market research industry as the technology for analyzing voice audio becomes more intelligent..
