TrueCoin tokens held in reserve will begin exchange listing following completion of the main token sale on April 1, 2018. Users, however, will not have to wait for the UTO to start earning TrueCoin. Prior to the exchange listings, the tokens will be available through participation in the UTO or through incentivized surveys via the True Reply platform and Alexa-powered devices..
