The UTO launches on March 1 at a token price of 1 Ethereum per 10,000 tokens. Pre-registration is open now and registration is required to participate in the sale..
`__ `__ `_______ `_ `____ ` `_ ` `____ `____ `_ ` 1_______ `__ `_____ `______ `_______________ `_ `___ `__ `__ `___________ `_ `_______ `_ `__________ `_ `__ `_____ 
There will be three caps: the "lite cap" of $500,000, to be equally split between bounties, marketing and founders' salaries; a "soft cap" of $5 million (35% for bounties/marketing, 35% for development, 20% for facilities, 10% for founders' salaries); and a "hard cap" of $20 million (50% for bounties/marketing, 40% for development, 5% for facilities and 5% for founders salaries.).
